  "number": 6481,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/6481",
  "title": "fix(vue): don't spread in ais-state-results",
  "body": "We no longer document directly using the `query` for example in the ais-state-results component, read it either from state or results.\r\n\r\nThe `connectStateResults` connector is removed, as we don't use it anymore but a `render` listener instead.\r\n\r\n[FX-3194]\r\n\r\nBREAKING CHANGE: connectStateResults is no longer exposed from Vue InstantSearch\r\nBREAKING CHANGE: the slot in ais-state-results receives an object with `results`, `state`, `status` and `error`, no longer direct access to e.g. `query`\r\n\n\n[FX-3194]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3194?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
